Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8年前  皇曆2009年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖布里塔尼亞帝國第十七王位繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修·Vi·布里塔尼亞殿下覲見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說瑪麗安娜皇妃在布里塔尼亞皇宮內遇害了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡可不是恐怖分子能輕易混進去的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 真正的犯人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕  可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事只是談論都令人恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過雖然母親被殺了 他還是很堅強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是魯魯修殿下已經沒有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身為後盾的阿斯福德家也完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的那位皇妹呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說雙腿中彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雙目也失明了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是因為受了心理創傷的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在那身體連作為政治道具都不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母后去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就為了這麼點小事而要求覲見布里塔尼亞皇帝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傳下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒時間陪小孩子胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼您沒有保護母親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您是皇帝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個國家最偉大的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼應該能夠保護她才對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也該見娜娜莉一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我對弱者不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是皇族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也不要什麼皇位繼承權了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了繼承你的皇位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷被捲入爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你自出生起就已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上穿的衣服到底是誰賜予你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住所  食物  甚至於生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是孤賜予你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你從來沒有靠自己活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  你卻如此的愚昧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經死了的你沒有什麼權利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與娜娜莉一起去日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇子和皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會是很好的交易籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}襲擊柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為第七代的KnightMare Frame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它的能力是一般機體的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說那個Lancelot的機師是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是名譽布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經將他從一等兵破格晉陞到准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也該覺得滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用依靠NUMBERS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一樣會贏!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為賭上性命去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才會有統治的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個道理我明白 皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連學校作業都要你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有上過普通的學校嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然學生會的同學也經常在學習上幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始我還有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是個很率直的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是擔心你能否和同學融洽相處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來也做好心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過碰巧我以前的朋友在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜那位朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的友情若能長久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再會就不是偶然 而是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 嘗嘗那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想聽聽你的感想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果醬?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄到了很不錯的藍梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 解散解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒有出場機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭  喜  各  位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然今天的課程已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是和朋友見面也是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我可以問你一件很重要的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔… 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮你… 是不是有什麼事情瞞著我們?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實也不必隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說出來吧 我不會驚訝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上次  我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和魯魯在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 上次你們在學校庭院內…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 那個是他擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是魯魯主動?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是上一次你也想要抓住這隻貓 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只不過是接吻而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是接吻而已?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你們做了比接吻更進一步的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快停止你那奇怪的聯想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太不會觀察情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  關於相親的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要重振阿斯福德家的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[ARAKAWA 荒川: 關東第二大河流 出海口是東京灣]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 分裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琦玉貧民區的包圍已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大和同盟的基地也在包圍圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,附近居民有半數以上都是他們的協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對於整個作戰勝算的影響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次為負0.2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在預算範圍內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,諸卿都參與了那次新宿的戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 多虧柯內莉婭殿下的高抬貴手 我們才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得很相似嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那時的新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,軍部針對恐怖分子出沒的琦玉貧民區
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,展開了包圍作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於柯內莉婭總督也親臨現場指揮作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故發佈了出入禁令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?  擺出這麼可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個小時後 總攻擊將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次作戰後  下一個區域將會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼連時間都要報導啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在向ZERO挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是激情型犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了把他引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意複製了與當時新宿一模一樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他是那種極度自負的性格的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會想來殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 總督的安危就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是榮譽與生命的爭奪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打算接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她都特意招待我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,況且 我還有事想問柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毀滅布里塔尼亞和找出殺害母親的兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為哪個更重要?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同等重要 這兩件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞皇族為了皇位繼承權不斷互相爭鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是被迫地爭鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是布里塔尼亞強大的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在爭鬥中活下來並取得勝利的最優秀之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將會成為下一任的皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者將失去一切任人踐踏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞就是這樣的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱肉強食是不可改變的自然法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是這樣  娜娜莉怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為弱小 所以不得不被放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會承認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来毁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[木天蓼：貓最喜歡的"草本興奮劑",逗貓專用]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我和魯魯修沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  魯魯修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會知道  那種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准去  魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在履行我們的契約之前你死了的話 我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的和在做的不是矛盾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是射傷你的腳  讓你乖乖地待在這裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法使用Geass啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這也早在預料之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自己可以使用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會來拜託我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為我會害怕槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在遇見你之前 只是個死人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是具屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻編造著仍然活著的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碌碌無為的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行屍走肉般的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和死亡沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果逼我回到從前的話 還不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確  毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡還有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個貧民區的人不但沒有通報恐怖分子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還包庇 窩藏他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是對國家的叛逆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對貧民區負責人的清理工作已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 時間還綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通報全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琦玉貧民區殲滅作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍  一級戰鬥戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼柯內莉婭殿下還不命令我們出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有ORANGE在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有被處分就該謝天謝地了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福 我們的前途都被斷送了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那是因為ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這種借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那學生真的是幫兇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,市外第四區鎮壓完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使由克洛維斯換成了柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪個部隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報上部隊名稱及ID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三偵查中隊  達利奧·托雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從恐怖分子手中拿到了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能幫忙聯繫一下總部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是光碟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 在此之前先讓我確認你的ID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請你交出你的Sutherland
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 小心使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外圍是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,埼京線無法突破嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有裝甲列車堵著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小路也無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赤羽或十條的援軍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注: 赤羽 十條 為埼京線上的兩個站點]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人還好說  團隊是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戶田和川口方面怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注: 戶田 川口 位於埼玉縣東南部]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那些…  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿事件你們應該也聽說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽從我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話你們就能獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B-12區鎮壓完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,F-7區未發現敵人蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,D-24…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,博瓦頓隊向516方向移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向516移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫ZERO的傢伙沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是個恐怖分子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和ZERO說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是把柯內莉婭引出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是製造個機會混進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R1 R2 後退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把敵人引到N-2的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7向兩點鐘方向射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P5小隊一起開始射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傑斯塔隊失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,G-47方面發現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西斯基隊正與敵方交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎遭遇伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人似乎捕獲了我軍的Sutherland \N並用來攻擊我軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和新宿的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了嗎  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N2就這樣向右上方攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R4射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N1向左邊那傢伙攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P3  把橋炸掉 切斷道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Point-17被毀壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里小隊失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下令全軍後退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續犧牲毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要退卻嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請恕直言 屬下還能繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣沒法戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向貧民區外延緊急撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無需整備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向貧民區外延緊急撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要混入撤退的部隊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭  輕易就能到你的身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,條件這麼快就齊備了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血緣真是不可否定的事實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這種類型可是很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟會走上哪條路呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來魯魯在這個AREA成立之前就在這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是鄰居嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯看上去總是一副不認真的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和努力這種東西完全無緣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話開始我一點也不喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在高一時 目睹了一起交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼看都是後面撞上來的人不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是誰也不去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯他呢 不為此驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有一笑了之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往地擺出一幅很無聊的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙到底在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然想要瞭解他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督是勝利的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的騎士吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵照您的旨意 不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我有Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在通常的警備條件下入侵還是太危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是要像克洛維斯那時一樣創造機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會活動室?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於貓祭的討論應該是在明天才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然卡蓮她說不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我總覺得她是為了矇混過關才假裝生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這種事還是直接問本人比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便也問問他對你是怎麼看的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊? 連這個也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的  一定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我來問的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 就是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 很痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真拚命啊  柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想用自己的親衛隊扭轉局勢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有N1恢復識別信號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,假裝成布里塔尼亞軍行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為誘餌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現一台發出信號的KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被留了在市外區域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法通信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出動救護隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消滅它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能成為敵人的人質了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經下令撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要無法執行命令的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算捨棄生命也要完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對於我的部下來說這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  你們不懂識別信號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不進行確認?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N2  發出識別信號 並往醫院廢墟方向撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R1  R2在那裡埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊追上來的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是信號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個地方前面有伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GLOUCESTER增援  包圍他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不追來?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R1  R2  中止埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GLOUCESTER到達指定地域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發現敵人蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看穿我的策略了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定對方真的是ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P2  N3  繞到敵人後方去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  快回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P2  N3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該死  B1  B5  你們去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是柯內莉婭的親衛隊 怎麼可能會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我們投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繞過我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P6  P8 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7  掩護N4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是B7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現其他獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先把對方幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7  聽從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這裡幹掉它的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,退下  敵人會從上面攻來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7  聽從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B8  報告你那裡的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還什麼情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B8
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的人 從P開始依次報告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍以第四隊形集合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被鎮壓了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼輕易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至連遊戲都稱不上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能像新宿那麼順利呢  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說這個只是個冒牌貨?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂了  反正很快就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是組織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全部KnightMare的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打開艙門 讓我看看你們的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部駕駛員打開艙門 讓我看看你們的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被檢查的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有ZERO的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真正身份也會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不直接看著對方是沒有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人在KnightMare裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能對步兵和其他駕駛員…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方的人數太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且怎樣才能讓他們都向我這裡看?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  也許可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要自稱是ZERO的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣的話  KnightMare就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  先發制人 強行突破?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以柯內莉婭的親衛隊為對手
