Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 那麼我來幫你打開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轉過身來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在立刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO! 發現ZERO了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然ZERO是這種性格嗎
