Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三  第五小隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,影像捕捉  確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能順水推舟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把他包圍起來  你們繞到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙擊部隊  射擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去了
