Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果朱雀在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是布里塔尼亞的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不在戰場上出戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是敵方的人
